  "slug": "angelos-hammers",
  "title": "Angelo's Hammers",
  "description": "A simple mod that adds hammers to mine in a 3x3 area",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f704925bb600b000edbf089522113a6f0a8e62ef.png\" />\n</div>\n\n<h2> </h2>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ABetancourt03/angelos-hammers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2b46c0e322b5ff09b298c17cdfe6833c826ac74a.png\" />\n </a>\n\n <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/angelos-hammers/gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/72e3a1583807c6def36ed7ad55d8d9ef5d07d7d2.png\" />\n    </a>\n\n <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/angelos-hammers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3494a91b8d02c32063e94ab08f6dd796b5bb4634.png\" />\n </a>\n\n <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/Q5Q71CX676\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4e525b7da08ae73392f08b3ef5da51ff72ef6889.png\" />\n </a>\n  \n  <div align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://fabricmc.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img width=\"191px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b5f2bbe24d378d863f70c8b4bf7bf9c0ef2b56f7.png\" />\n </a>\n\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c4f1a960f18ab198a516e9e092572e3d4be63879.png\" />\n  </a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h2>Also works in Forge and NeoForge</h2>\n  <strong>¡¡IMPORTANT!!</strong>\n  <p>For Forge only works on 1.20.1.</p>\n  <p>And for NeoForge on 1.20.1, 1.21 and 1.21.1.</p>\n\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img width=\"300px\"  src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/538973c835bf323d8b0048512d61c0ff8aa30f0b.png\" />\n  </a>\n\n <div align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forgified-fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img  src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/167dc4a406313cb19c2e4bd1493d74180ab8c591.png\" />\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector-extras\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img  src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/81c4efc44654ac0db30652242292978d25f882b1.png\" />\n  </a>\n </div>\n\n  <h3>For Fabric only requires Fabric API.</h3>\n</div>\n\n<h2> </h2>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h4>Angelo's Hammers is a simple mod that adds various type of hammers to mine a 3x3 area.</h4>\n  \n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3830924d0e92932032a302990766255db704b405.png\"/>\n</div>\n\n<br></br>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/dd089b6d8a477084782e03816571059cd429c863_0.webp\" />\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h2>Hammers Recipes</h2>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h3>Wooden Hammer</h3>\n  <p>You can use any type of planks to craft the Wooden Hammer.</p>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/71a9c17812e39273a4810038f8d00b7ef165166b.png\" />\n\n  <p>Even using various types at the same time.</p>\n  \n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/37758a690a00fa44475fd5e08d7de3ab856181c2.png\" />\n\n  <h3>Stone Hammer</h3>\n  <p>Like the Wooden Hammer, you can use any vanilla stone crafting for this.</p>\n\n <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6d8c9b04552044824e6d68b582947012291de9f0.png\" />\n\n  <h3>Golden Hammer</h3>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b8168cc1d8823c650668e2376545848ceac7e192.png\" />\n\n  <h3>Diamond Hammer</h3>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7e877f98b9a787c7b476e6bd06ebd877a4cc1682.png\" />\n\n  <h3>Netherite Hammer</h3>\n  <p>Using the <strong>smithing table</strong>, a <strong>netherite upgrade</strong>, the <strong>diamond hammer</strong> and one <strong>netherite ingot</strong> you will get the netherite upgrade for the Diamond Hammer.</p>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/347f3d9f46805c4185100904b4bcf3902e96a081.png\" />\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h2>Enchanting the Hammers</h2>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <p>You can enchant the hammers with all the vanilla enchantments available for the pickaxe.</p>\n  \n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/97a7dbb21f7d65647601ea95dba389e318521604.png\" />\n\n  <p>Then you can enchant them at the enchanting table as well.</p>\n    \n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/795cf07ccbb96a5f13d9f2ef1c2a880a8aceb889.png\" />\n\n  <p>Also, you can repair and enchant them at the anvil like you do with the vanilla tools.</p>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1e47347999ea8cd80f189220cb78501eafe275dc.png\" />\n</div>",
